What's Inside

SCIENCE-BACKED
INGREDIENTS

Powerful, well-researched ingredients selected to create a functional formula that works in harmony with your body.

Full Ingredient List

Filtered Water, Sweetener Blend (Erythritol, Monk Fruit Extract), β-Cyclodextrin, Lime Powder, Hovenia Dulcis Extract, L-Cysteine, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate, Citric Acid, Natural Flavours, Maltodextrin.

🌿

Hovenia Dulcis

Known as the Japanese Raisin Tree — studied for its role in supporting the body's response to alcohol and promoting liver wellness.

🧬

L-Cysteine

An amino acid precursor to glutathione — one of the body's most important antioxidants, assisting in natural detoxification processes.

Our Story

BALANCING SOCIAL
LIFE & WELL-BEING

Proudly developed in Malaysia, our mission is to create innovative, science-aware products with integrity. AlcoReset+ is our first step — and we're excited to expand our vision for post-social wellness across Southeast Asia and beyond.

Questions

FREQUENTLY
ASKED QUESTIONS

What is Thirst8 – AlcoReset+?+
AlcoReset+ is a functional beverage designed to support your body's natural processes after social drinking. It is a non-alcoholic, low-sugar, citrus-lime flavoured drink formulated with ingredients like Hovenia Dulcis and L-Cysteine.
Is this a hangover cure?+
No. AlcoReset+ is not a medical product, treatment, or cure for hangovers. It is a functional beverage that supports general wellness and next-day freshness as part of a balanced and responsible lifestyle. It does not prevent intoxication, and we encourage responsible consumption of alcohol.
Is it approved by NPRA/KKM in Malaysia?+
AlcoReset+ is classified as a beverage, not a drug or health supplement. It is produced in compliance with food safety standards and its formulation is aligned with guidelines for beverages in Malaysia. It does not require NPRA/KKM registration like medical products do.
What do the key ingredients do?+
Hovenia Dulcis and L-Cysteine are included for their roles in supporting liver wellness, assisting the body's natural antioxidant systems, and supporting the metabolism of alcohol byproducts. They work together to promote overall balance.
What are the full ingredients?+
Filtered Water, Sweetener Blend (Erythritol, Monk Fruit Extract), β-Cyclodextrin, Lime Powder, Hovenia Dulcis Extract, L-Cysteine, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate, Citric Acid, Natural Flavours, and Maltodextrin. We focus on a low-sugar formula with functional ingredients.
When should I drink it?+
For best results, we recommend drinking one can of AlcoReset+ after your last alcoholic beverage or before you go to sleep.
